											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="In the distance, screams. A wide shot over the city shows mists rolling through the streets, quenching all light. Where the mists pass, the blazing red eyes of vampire spawn bloom in the shadows. &#xD;&#xA;Soon the city is shrouded in darkness but for the single blazing beacon that is Astarion." />
